I am making a quadruped using 8 MG90S serovs, an ESP32-C3-Super-Mini and a PCA9685 Servo Driver Board.
I started this project because I like making things and this also coincides with my school robotics club.
This is a way of proving myself, gaining experience and making fun stuff as well.
